{"tid":2346313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣出現首起英國變種病毒！案792英返台發燒少年病毒比對結果出爐","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T08:10:06.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff8cd9665d4c274d767a5d7f55bbc6010e23937","tid":2346313,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"嚴防英國變種病毒，我國已針對英國入境進行加強防疫，並對近期自英國入境染疫個案進行病毒基因序列比對，指揮中心指揮官陳時中今（30）日證實國內出現首宗英國變種病毒，正是首班倫敦飛台北班機發燒的10多歲少年。<br />\n<br />\n國內從12月23日開始針對有英國旅遊史者加強檢疫，過去14天有英國旅遊史者必須集中檢疫，入境與期滿皆須採檢，倫敦飛返台北的客機航班數將減半，機組員須居家檢疫14天，期滿前進行採檢陰性及自主健康管理7天後再進入社區等。<br />\n<br />\n27日晚間首班倫敦飛台北班機共127人(含機組員13人)抵達，該團總計有3人確診，其中1人為10多歲少年出現發燒送醫，28日確定染疫，研判發病日即為登機日，登機兩度前量測並未發燒；其餘2人無症狀。另採檢近期從英國返國者，也有1名染疫，指揮中心正在進行相關病毒基因序列比對，釐清是否變異病毒。<br />\n<br />\n陳時中今日公布病毒比對結果，該名發燒少年證實為英國變種病毒，等於是第一個案例到了台灣。所幸從機上開始有適當防護，至於檢驗到醫院，現在在院治療中，有相關輕微症狀並不嚴重，其餘同班機無特別情況，持續觀察中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201230/1887892.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201230%2F1887892.htm&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=c8636f12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201230/1887892.htm</a>"},{"pid":"91b5ee51d79aac83b33bf73c681ef8e0c0c6d2d5","tid":2346313,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:23:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f3bc1a2487dce4af2213f26b2fa946ac675e8cb","tid":2346313,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"台灣影衰晒中國 我地中國防疫一直做得好<br />\n而家唯有暫緩武統"},{"pid":"bb7057c24529774b1dd26e783f87055d360733b5","tid":2346313,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"起你老母"},{"pid":"e91584d306a35b7c5223634f5c016d0317260e5d","tid":2346313,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb7057c24529774b1dd26e783f87055d360733b5","tid":2346313,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"起你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"我照copy台灣新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31531542774cae49669869c44d44b2c614c148a7","tid":2346313,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯762"},{"pid":"fb933737c8c892629fff4dbfc7dc1f9c077d103d","tid":2346313,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"英你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5750780c91ddaac4bd5118b8e9daf0cf02b9c33a","tid":2346313,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"成日話去英國班廢物唔該嗱嗱聲去啦"},{"pid":"c9b35dd3cd535785aeb3f6eff3a8050bb28e11a2","tid":2346313,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:10:06.000Z","msg":"唔一早禁英國機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}